To make use of the distuils extension add the following line to the beginning
of your setup.py:

from Snippets.distutils import build_plus, build_l10n

Add the following option to setup call:

cmdclass = { "build" : build_plus,
             "build_l10n" :  build_l10n }

And set the following options in your setup.cfg:

[build]
l10n=True
